Your progress in the game is tracked by achievements. There are are 6 of them in total. You get them by spelling words correctly (on your first attempt in "New Quiz"), or by obtaining streaks of a specific length (getting a certain number of words right in a row).

When you unlock the achivement, the "View Reward" button for it becomes unlocke. You can click on it, and the video reward for you to watch will appear. The achievements will lead you to a special surprise.
